data.description: Discover comfort and convenience in this charming 2-bed, 2.5-bath townhome within a secure gated Amber Pointe community. Step inside to find a sleek first floor adorned with large ceramic tiles, seamlessly connecting the great room—integrating living, kitchen, and dining areas. The kitchen features an extended breakfast bar, perfect for entertaining. A thoughtfully upgraded half bath on the first floor adds convenience. Upstairs, find laundry facilities, a master, and a guest bedroom. The master bath offers a garden tub and a separate shower stall for a spa-like retreat. Parking is a breeze with an extra-long driveway accommodating three cars. Enjoy community amenities like an in-ground pool and scattered playgrounds. Benefit from HOA ease, covering lawn maintenance and irrigation.  Conveniently located near attractions, Highway 192, shopping centers, and the Florida Turnpike.  This isn't just a home; it's a chance to embrace comfort and sophistication. Don't miss the  opportunity to make this Kissimmee townhome your haven in the heart of Central Florida!
